               <p>Before Mr. Justice Bayley.</p>
               <p>12. 
               
                  <persName id="t18221204-12-defend133" type="defendantName">
                     MARGARET 
                     GIBBONS
                  <interp inst="t18221204-12-defend133" type="surname" value="GIBBONS"></interp>
